review: Kenalog-40 (triamcinolone):I have Tunnel syndrome in my foot. A doctor made my Kenalog injection in it.  I could not feel my foot during five days. It's been three weeks now, but I have numbness and  tingling .  And I do not know when will finish numbness and tingling....If finishes at all...
Acetocot (triamcinolone):this drug worked for me but is very slow
